p.d: Julien has left without warning. Each reacts in their own way: Sylvie notifies the police of his disappearance, Jacques concentrates on his departure to avoid getting involved, and Marie has enormous difficulty in keeping their break-up a secret, not to mention Julie's identity... Directed by: Stephen Cafiero (season 3, France, 2019) Screenplay: Frédéric Rosset, Camille Rosset Cast: Sébastien Chassagne (Julien), Marie Kauffmann (Marie), Théo Fernandez (Jacques), Nathalie Cerda (Sylvie), Matilda Marty (Emma), Allison Chassagne (Julie), Charlie Nelson (Louis), Amel Charif (Sam), Julie Farenc-Deramond (Léa), Martin Judas (Dylan), Bruni Makaya (Yanis) Genre: comedy drama
